title: APARTMENT FOR RENT IN COLLIERVILLE w/pool #10
map_address: 325 S Center St near South St
app_fee: $60 application fee per adult for background, credit check and processing
posting_body: This renovated apartment unit is in a great neighborhood in Collierville.
It's down the street from the Old Town Square, where there's plenty of retail shopping and restaurants.
It's also not far from Highway 385, and not to mention the amazing Collierville school district.
The apartment comes with a clean community swimming pool, plenty of gated parking, on-site laundry facilities, central heat and air, and a very quiet and comfortable living space.
The unit is 850 sqft and has 2 beds and one bath.
It comes with a fridge, oven/range and a dishwasher.
There's new carpet in the living room and bedrooms and beautiful vinyl flooring in the kitchen.
Come check it out before it's gone!
See attached YouTube video link below to see the inside of the apartment.
